[aternity_rest_api_summary://<name>]
global_account = Username (must have the OData REST API role) and its password, you can find this by logging into Aternity >> selecting User icon > REST API Access.
aternity_domain_name = Example: If your URL is <https://my-aternity.aternity.com>, then only input "my-aternity" in this field
rest_api_name = For the latest version of the Aternity APIs list please visit "https://help.aternity.com/restapi"Example Rest_api name looks like "CONNECTION_TEST" OR "DEVICE_INVENTORY" OR "DEVICE_HEALTH_RAW" etc.